          "publishedAt": "2023-06-23T09:54:19Z",
          "channelId": "UCNDmCdgaRH6qbMQiw34KywQ",
          "title": "Capital Markets Day 2022 - webcast",
          "description": "On June 22nd 2022, at Umicore Capital Markets Day, Mathias Miedreich, CEO, along with members of the management presented our strategic roadmap towards 2030. We provided further insights on our ambitions and the next exciting chapter of our journey of sustainable growth and value creation.\n\nRead more here: https://capitalmarketsday.umicore.com/en/\n\nAgenda & Speakers\n00:00 - 05:19 Agenda\n05:20 - 01:00:38  Excellent starting position and strategy drivers (Mathias Miedreich, Frank Daufenbach)\n01:00:39 - 01:33:35 Growth, returns and cash-flows (Filip Platteeuw)\n01:33:36 - 02:10:28 Q&A session with Mathias, Frank and Filip\n02:10:29 - 02:33:40 We go for zero (G\u00e9raldine Nolens)\n02:33:42 - 03:06:48 Advanced materials as a key enabling technology in various sectors (Denis Goffaux)\n03:06:49 - 03:26:18 Q&A Session with Mathias, G\u00e9raldine and Denis\n03:26:24 - 04:08:28 Mobility transformation - Capture profitable growth and create sustainable value in Rechargeable Battery Materials (Ralph Kiessling)\n04:08:29 - 04:32:31 Mobility transformation - Capture peak profitability and maximize value in Automotive Catalysts (Bart Sap)\n04:32:32 - 05:19:14 Q&A session with Mathias, Ralph and Bart\n05:19:15 - 05:34:24 Mobility transformation - Capture the emerging growth in Fuel Cell (Bart Sap)\n05:34:25 - 06:06:11 Mobility transformation - Capture profitable growth in circular battery value chain with Battery Recycling Solutions (Kurt Vandeputte)\n06:06:12 -  06:35:23 Q&A session with Mathias, Bart and Kurt\n06:35:37 - 06:39:47 Closing remarks (Mathias Miedreich)",
